description: The girl was killed by a stray bullet in a drive-by shooting that went wrong, media reports say.
title: Sweden: Death of girl, 12, ignites debate over gang violence
title_page: Sweden: Death of girl, 12, ignites debate over gang violence - BBC News
maintext: Details of what happened have not been officially confirmed, but local media outlets reported that the gunmen had been aiming at two members of a criminal gang, and had not intended to shoot the child.
